## The Bezel Advantage

The bezel is not just more protective. It is also cleaner. The emerald cut's rectangular outline stays completely visible. No prong silhouettes interrupt the profile of the stone from any angle.

At every carat size, the bezel stud costs less than the prong version. The savings column in the table below shows exactly how much.

